description: Divio Technologies AB operates as a Cloud Management Software development platform. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 14 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2019-12-18. The firm focuses on developing cloud Web application. The firm offers Divio platform, which simplifies cloud hosting, deployment and development via a proprietary Platform as a Service (PaaS) solution. The platform allows enterprises to significantly reduce cost, time to market and decreases dependencies on employees as well as cloud vendors. The firm has offices in Sweden and throughout the world.
